{"tid":233123,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人爸爸係咁（求解決方法）","createTime":"2017-05-07T10:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T11:48:42.000Z","uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf590da3f81c8e52f0c1f83ab5fc741e164497c","tid":233123,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"Sorry too long for 19999<br />\n背景：公屋，單親家庭，工作酒樓經理<br />\n每次到左賭馬日子就好像撞邪咁，只要有人阻住佢或者嘈佢，就會破口大罵，你地都知到公屋細，叫佢讓過小小都比佢小，又話嘈到佢同搞到佢，輸左又會話人地累輸佢，仲特登選跑馬日子黎放假，無跑馬既日子會不停講好難聽既說話比人聽，仲要叫極都唔會停⋯<br />\n利申近幾年先係咁（我細個果時係慈父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n各位巴絲有無方法可令我爸爸變返以前咁？"},{"pid":"46e0396f4ab95a998369ccc57090a8352d3cf4a6","tid":233123,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"同佢講<br />\n&quot;借一借都唔得，輸唔切咩&quot;<br />\n&quot;睇你成個輸相，算撚數啦，慳返袋落袋啦&quot;"},{"pid":"6417ad8ebc44643f6ecc61cc2705efd8ce5b6744","tid":233123,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"寫逢賭必輸係塊鏡，等佢刷牙見到"},{"pid":"1ed79790cdeec9ac79d76f4c4a5323c04cc476ba","tid":233123,"uid":56873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"自己都賭馬，同佢有共同話題，之後2個男人坐底慢慢傾掂佢"},{"pid":"35b863a724b674291d94e57362f7ba6645ac8973","tid":233123,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"爸爸"},{"pid":"9ec81e7f887395307fb611a902ed391b83bf4716","tid":233123,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"佢賭身家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8301e38e55736359882dc4bb160be19baab715","tid":233123,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"拍佢膊頭祝佢贏多d"},{"pid":"c492c2db9ca23edbe318d4377bda9389a04c5273","tid":233123,"uid":653,"like":0,