504","tid":233123,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫做叫佢讓過小小都比佢小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用詞用得唔好，應該係讓開小小都比佢鬧"},{"pid":"4a1bf2000a1efe5e1a7dfb798bbc63f38ca8b56d","tid":233123,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫逢賭必輸係塊鏡，等佢刷牙見到</blockquote><br />\n實會比佢咒罵到訓覺都keep住鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78f9a3871e52445651e4993e61a4243ec2246bb","tid":233123,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"466d1cebcb56bd0d706c607b7ea3844e7a8e62f1","tid":233123,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢賭身家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每次隻10$？咩咩連贏位位置q?唔清楚，但每次都輸成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一星期跑2次馬一個月跑8次<br />\n咁咪輸1個月糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f49c41112252b0ac2e8b1d8cd42942415bf6b57","tid":233123,"uid":87680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢賭身家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每次隻10$？咩咩連贏位位置q?唔清楚，但每次都輸成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一星期跑2次馬一個月跑8次<br />\n咁咪輸1個月糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得佢好癲，成日話儲錢咩咩咩，最後咩都無儲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb6c0f19d7bcbe2678d82f8a138f5127232ddb2","tid":233123,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"以前我老豆都類似係咁<br />\n我好細個時佢都好錫我<br />\n唔賭時還